      caption="<span class='font-semibold text-accent-magenta'>Macrophages</span> (magenta) phagocytosing <span class='font-semibold text-accent-yellow'>TME-derived injected myelin</span> (yellow) to become lipid-laden macrophages, imaged in live zebrafish embryos starting 2h (left) and 24h post-injection (right). Forn-Cuní, unpublished, 2025."
    />
  </Section>

